===Etymology===
From Persian {{FAchar|[[چادر]]}} ''čâdor''.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[loose]] [[black]] [[robe]], made from a single [[cloth]], worn as a [[combination]] [[head]] [[covering]], [[veil]] and [[shawl]] by [[Muslim]] [[women]], especially in [[Iran]].

